				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${V}_{{{{{{\rm{Cu}}}}}}}^{0}$$\end{document}) recombination is more efficient in the CuI thin film TPA in I2 due to its higher density of VCu0\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
